  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个金融科技系统的流程图，核心是支付网关和欺诈检测的交互。我想把PaymentGateway拆成两个实例，一个叫Audit，一个叫Define，分别处理审计和配置功能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PaymentGateway拆成Audit和Define两个节点。那交易队列怎么处理？需要单独一个节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，交易队列叫Bail，FinTech_TransactionQueue。然后欺诈检测引擎也需要两个实例，一个叫Barg，一个叫Code，都是FinTech_FraudDetection，一个负责实时拦截，一个负责规则定义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把六个节点都加上：Audit、Bail、Barg、Code、Define，还有你提到的Risk和Signal、Place、Press这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连线关系我理一下：Audit要连到Define，表示审计结果反馈给配置模块；Bail和Barg要双向连接，交易队列和欺诈检测是互相调用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Audit→Define，然后Bail↔Barg双向，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。另外Code要连Define，欺诈检测的规则定义要同步给支付网关配置；Define还要连Barg，配置信息要传给欺诈检测引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code→Define和Define→Barg。还有Risk、Signal、Place这些节点，它们的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Risk是风险信号源，要连到Signal；Signal再连到Barg，表示风险信号最终进入欺诈检测。Place和Press是另一个子流程，Place直接触发Press动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Risk→Signal→Barg，以及Place→Press。我检查一下整体结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Signal连Barg的方向我刚才说反了，应该是Signal指向Barg，但我是想让Barg接收Signal，所以方向是对的。不过再确认下：Risk到Signal，Signal到Barg，这个流向没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下所有连线：Audit→Define、Bail↔Barg双向、Code→Define、Define→Barg、Risk→Signal、Signal→Barg、Place→Press。一共七组关系，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个结构。PaymentGateway通过Audit和Define两个视角接入，TransactionQueue通过Bail和欺诈检测双向交互，加上风险信号链和独立的Place-Press流程，完整了。",
